overview.en: The FIG (Future intelligence) open source community is an open platform for decentralized blockchain technology to promote data interconnection, transaction settlement, and intelligent contracts between the Internet of Things and AI robots. Today, human beings have entered the AI era, and AI can speak, listen, see, move, think, and approach human level. The goal of the FIG community is to connect FIG technology between AI, the Internet of Things, and data. Through smart contracts and property transactions, human beings are the real beneficiaries of the wealth of the Internet of Things and AI robots.
overview.zh: FIG（Future intelligence）Open source community is a decentralized blockchain technology open platform aimed at promoting data interconnection, transaction settlement and smart contract between the Internet of things and AI robots. Today, human beings have entered the age of AI. AI can speak, listen, see, move and think, approaching the level of human beings. The goal of the fig community is to connect AI, Internet of things and data by using fig technology, and make human beings become the real beneficiaries of the Internet of things and AI robot wealth through smart contracts and property rights transactions.
